<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <title>AmicBridge – Private Lending for Verified People</title>
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
  <meta
    name="description"
    content="AmicBridge is a private, identity-verified network where serious borrowers and lenders connect directly."
  />
  <style>
    :root {
      --bg: #f5f7fb;
      --bg-card: #ffffff;
      --text-main: #111827;
      --text-muted: #6b7280;
      --accent: #4f46e5;
      --accent-soft: rgba(79, 70, 229, 0.08);
      --border-subtle: #e5e7eb;
      --shadow-soft: 0 18px 40px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.08);
      --radius-lg: 14px;
      --radius-xl: 22px;
      --font-sans:
        system-ui,
        -apple-system,
        BlinkMacSystemFont,
        "Segoe UI",
        sans-serif;
    }

    * {
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    html,
    body {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      font-family: var(--font-sans);
      color: var(--text-main);
      background: var(--bg);
    }

    body {
      -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
    }

    a {
      color: inherit;
      text-decoration: none;
    }

    /* Layout */

    .page {
      min-height: 100vh;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
    }

    .container {
      width: 100%;
      max-width: 1080px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 0 20px;
    }

    /* Header */

    .header {
      position: sticky;
      top: 0;
      z-index: 20;
      backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
      background: rgba(245, 247, 251, 0.9);
      border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(229, 231, 235, 0.9);
    }

    .header-inner {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
      padding: 14px 0;
    }

    .logo {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 10px;
    }

    .logo-mark {
      width: 32px;
      height: 32px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #4f46e5, #7c3aed);
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      color: #fff;
      font-weight: 600;
      font-size: 18px;
      box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(79, 70, 229, 0.5);
    }

    .logo-text-main {
      font-weight: 600;
      font-size: 18px;
      letter-spacing: 0.01em;
    }

    .logo-text-sub {
      font-size: 12px;
      color: var(--text-muted);
    }

    .nav {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 20px;
      font-size: 14px;
      color: var(--text-muted);
    }

    .nav a {
      padding: 6px 0;
      border-bottom: 1px solid transparent;
    }

    .nav a:hover {
      border-bottom-color: rgba(79, 70, 229, 0.6);
      color: #111827;
    }

    .nav-cta {
      padding: 7px 16px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      border: 1px solid var(--border-subtle);
      background: #ffffff;
      font-weight: 500;
      color: #111827;
    }

    .nav-cta:hover {
      border-color: var(--accent);
      box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.08);
    }

    /* Hero */

    .hero {
      padding: 60px 0 56px;
    }

    .hero-inner {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 3.2fr) minmax(0, 2.8fr);
      gap: 40px;
      align-items: center;
    }

    .eyebrow {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 8px;
      padding: 4px 10px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: var(--accent-soft);
      color: #4338ca;
      font-size: 11px;
      font-weight: 600;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.08em;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
    }

    .eyebrow-dot {
      width: 6px;
      height: 6px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: #4f46e5;
    }

    .hero-title {
      font-size: clamp(30px, 4vw, 40px);
      line-height: 1.1;
      letter-spacing: -0.03em;
      margin: 0 0 16px;
    }

    .hero-subtitle {
      margin: 0 0 18px;
      color: var(--text-muted);
      font-size: 15px;
      line-height: 1.6;
      max-width: 520px;
    }

    .hero-note {
      font-size: 13px;
      color: var(--text-muted);
      margin-bottom: 24px;
    }

    .hero-actions {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 12px;
      margin-bottom: 22px;
    }

    .btn {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      padding: 11px 18px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      border: 1px solid transparent;
      font-size: 14px;
      font-weight: 500;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition:
        background 0.15s ease,
        color 0.15s ease,
        box-shadow 0.15s ease,
        transform 0.05s ease;
      text-align: center;
      white-space: nowrap;
    }

    .btn-primary {
      background: #4f46e5;
      color: #ffffff;
      box-shadow: 0 14px 35px rgba(79, 70, 229, 0.45);
    }

    .btn-primary:hover {
      background: #4338ca;
      transform: translateY(-1px);
      box-shadow: 0 18px 40px rgba(79, 70, 229, 0.5);
    }

    .btn-secondary {
      background: #ffffff;
      color: #111827;
      border-color: var(--border-subtle);
    }

    .btn-secondary:hover {
      border-color: var(--accent);
      box-shadow: 0 12px 28px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.08);
      transform: translateY(-1px);
    }

    .hero-footnote {
      font-size: 11px;
      color: var(--text-muted);
      max-width: 420px;
      line-height: 1.5;
    }

    /* Hero side card */

    .hero-card {
      background: var(--bg-card);
      border-radius: var(--radius-xl);
      box-shadow: var(--shadow-soft);
      padding: 20px 20px 18px;
      border: 1px solid rgba(229, 231, 235, 0.9);
    }

    .hero-card-header {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
      margin-bottom: 18px;
    }

    .hero-card-title {
      font-size: 14px;
      font-weight: 600;
    }

    .hero-card-tag {
      font-size: 11px;
      padding: 3px 8px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: #eef2ff;
      color: #4338ca;
      border: 1px solid #e0e7ff;
    }

    .hero-card-row {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 14px;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
      font-size: 13px;
    }

    .hero-card-label {
      color: var(--text-muted);
    }

    .hero-card-value {
      font-weight: 500;
    }

    .hero-card-divider {
      border-top: 1px dashed #e5e7eb;
      margin: 10px 0 12px;
    }

    .badge-row {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 8px;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }

    .small-badge {
      padding: 4px 8px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
      background: #f9fafb;
      font-size: 11px;
      color: #6b7280;
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 4px;
    }

    .small-badge-dot {
      width: 6px;
      height: 6px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: #10b981;
    }

    .hero-card-footer {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
      margin-top: 6px;
      font-size: 11px;
      color: var(--text-muted);
    }

    /* Sections */

    .section {
      padding: 12px 0 40px;
    }

    .section-header {
      margin-bottom: 18px;
    }

    .section-kicker {
      font-size: 11px;
      font-weight: 600;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.08em;
      color: #6b7280;
      margin-bottom: 6px;
    }

    .section-title {
      font-size: 20px;
      margin: 0 0 4px;
      letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    }

    .section-subtitle {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 14px;
      color: var(--text-muted);
      max-width: 520px;
    }

    .section-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0, 1fr));
      gap: 18px;
    }

    .card {
      background: #ffffff;
      border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
      padding: 16px 16px 15px;
      border: 1px solid var(--border-subtle);
      font-size: 13px;
    }

    .card-title {
      font-weight: 600;
      margin-bottom: 6px;
      font-size: 14px;
    }

    .card p {
      margin: 0;
      color: var(--text-muted);
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    /* Disclaimer / footer */

    .disclaimer {
      padding: 20px 0 40px;
      font-size: 11px;
      color: #6b7280;
    }

    .disclaimer-inner {
      background: #f3f4ff;
      border-radius: 16px;
      padding: 14px 14px 13px;
      border: 1px solid #e0e7ff;
      line-height: 1.5;
    }

    .footer {
      padding: 16px 0 28px;
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #9ca3af;
      border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
      margin-top: auto;
    }

    .footer-inner {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 10px;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      align-items: center;
    }

    .footer-links {
      display: flex;
      gap: 14px;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }

    .footer a {
      color: inherit;
    }

    .footer a:hover {
      color: #6b7280;
    }

    /* Responsive */

    @media (max-width: 860px) {
      .hero-inner {
        grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1fr);
      }

      .hero-card {
        order: -1;
      }

      .header-inner {
        gap: 12px;
      }

      .nav {
        display: none; /* simple mobile header; expand later if needed */
      }

      .hero {
        padding-top: 36px;
      }
    }

    @media (max-width: 640px) {
      .section-grid {
        grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1fr);
      }

      .hero-actions {
        flex-direction: column;
        align-items: stretch;
      }

      .btn {
        width: 100%;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="page">
    <!-- Header -->
    <header class="header">
      <div class="container header-inner">
        <div class="logo">
          <div class="logo-mark">A</div>
          <div>
            <div class="logo-text-main">AmicBridge</div>
            <div class="logo-text-sub">Private lending network</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <nav class="nav">
          <a href="#how-it-works">How it works</a>
          <a href="#trust">Trust &amp; identity</a>
          <a href="#borrow">Borrow</a>
          <a href="#lend">Lend</a>
          <a href="#strategy">Strategy</a>
          <a class="nav-cta" href="#contact">Contact</a>
        </nav>
      </div>
    </header>

    <!-- Hero -->
    <main>
      <section class="hero">
        <div class="container hero-inner">
          <div>
            <div class="eyebrow">
              <span class="eyebrow-dot"></span>
              Private, invitation-based network
            </div>
            <h1 class="hero-title">
              Private lending for serious, verified people.
            </h1>
            <p class="hero-subtitle">
              AmicBridge is a private peer-to-peer network where verified borrowers and verified lenders
              connect directly. No anonymous profiles, no pooled funds, and no unrealistic promises.
            </p>
            <p class="hero-note">
              Every member is reviewed and identity-verified before entering the network. Our focus is on
              who you are and how clearly you explain your plans.
            </p>
            <div class="hero-actions">
              <a class="btn btn-primary" href="#borrow">Request a loan</a>
              <a class="btn btn-secondary" href="#lend">Offer lending</a>
            </div>
            <p class="hero-footnote">
              AmicBridge is a bridge, not a bank. Members speak directly to each other, set their own
              terms, and move funds wallet-to-wallet once they are comfortable.
            </p>
          </div>

          <!-- Side "trust" card -->
          <aside class="hero-card" aria-label="Example of verified borrower profile">
            <div class="hero-card-header">
              <div>
                <div class="hero-card-title">Verified member profile (example)</div>
              </div>
              <div class="hero-card-tag">Identity checked</div>
            </div>

            <div class="hero-card-row">
              <div>
                <div class="hero-card-label">Borrower</div>
                <div class="hero-card-value">Anna K., architect</div>
              </div>
              <div>
                <div class="hero-card-label">Location</div>
                <div class="hero-card-value">Oslo, Norway</div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="hero-card-row">
              <div>
                <div class="hero-card-label">Seeking</div>
                <div class="hero-card-value">65,000 NOK · 12 months</div>
              </div>
              <div>
                <div class="hero-card-label">Purpose</div>
                <div class="hero-card-value">Home renovation</div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="hero-card-divider"></div>

            <p style="font-size: 12px; margin: 0 0 10px; color: #4b5563;">
              “I am renovating a small apartment and need short-term liquidity. I am prepared to share
              invoices, a clear repayment plan, and my professional background.”
            </p>

            <div class="badge-row">
              <span class="small-badge">
                <span class="small-badge-dot"></span>
                Passport &amp; BankID verified
              </span>
              <span class="small-badge">Professional profile linked</span>
              <span class="small-badge">Private 1:1 conversation before agreement</span>
            </div>

            <div class="hero-card-footer">
              <span>Example only. Not a live offer.</span>
              <span>Identity first. Money second.</span>
            </div>
          </aside>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- How it works -->
      <section id="how-it-works" class="section">
        <div class="container">
          <div class="section-header">
            <div class="section-kicker">How it works</div>
            <h2 class="section-title">A private process built around identity.</h2>
            <p class="section-subtitle">
              AmicBridge focuses on who is entering the network before any money moves. Every step is
              simple, structured, and aimed at serious, transparent people.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="section-grid">
            <div class="card">
              <div class="card-title">1. Identity and background</div>
              <p>
                Prospective members share personal identity details and high-level background information.
                We review this before granting access. Anonymous or incomplete applications are not
                accepted.
              </p>
            </div>
            <div class="card">
              <div class="card-title">2. Clear, written requests</div>
              <p>
                Borrowers describe what they want to borrow, why, and how they plan to repay. Lenders
                outline what type of requests they are open to. Clarity comes before numbers.
              </p>
            </div>
            <div class="card">
              <div class="card-title">3. Direct connections</div>
              <p>
                Once both sides are comfortable, they speak privately and directly. Any agreement is made
                person-to-person. Funds move wallet-to-wallet or account-to-account, never via AmicBridge.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Trust & identity -->
      <section id="trust" class="section">
        <div class="container">
          <div class="section-header">
            <div class="section-kicker">Trust &amp; identity</div>
            <h2 class="section-title">Designed for transparent, responsible adults.</h2>
            <p class="section-subtitle">
              The goal is not maximum volume, but a curated network of people who are comfortable being
              known, verified, and clear about their intentions.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="section-grid">
            <div class="card">
              <div class="card-title">Verification before access</div>
              <p>
                Every member is screened and identity-verified before they see private requests or offers.
                This reduces anonymous risk and keeps the network focused on long-term reliability.
              </p>
            </div>
            <div class="card">
              <div class="card-title">Transparency over hype</div>
              <p>
                AmicBridge does not market “passive income” or guaranteed returns. Instead, it provides
                enough information for careful people to make their own decisions.
              </p>
            </div>
            <div class="card">
              <div class="card-title">Reputation that grows</div>
              <p>
                Over time, successful interactions and consistent behaviour can support a stronger
                reputation in the network. Members who act professionally stand out naturally.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Borrow -->
      <section id="borrow" class="section">
        <div class="container">
          <div class="section-header">
            <div class="section-kicker">Borrow</div>
            <h2 class="section-title">Request a loan from people, not algorithms.</h2>
            <p class="section-subtitle">
              Present a clear plan, show who you are, and speak directly with lenders who understand your
              situation.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="section-grid">
            <div class="card">
              <div class="card-title">Explain your purpose</div>
              <p>
                Share what you need, why you need it, and how you intend to repay. The more transparent
                you are, the easier it is for the right lender to engage.
              </p>
            </div>
            <div class="card">
              <div class="card-title">Speak directly</div>
              <p>
                Once a lender is interested, you talk directly. No automated matching, no public auctions,
                no pressure. Just a private, professional conversation.
              </p>
            </div>
            <div class="card">
              <div class="card-title">Decide at your own pace</div>
              <p>
                You are free to decline, renegotiate, or walk away if you are not comfortable. AmicBridge
                does not push, advise, or enforce any agreement.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Lend -->
      <section id="lend" class="section">
        <div class="container">
          <div class="section-header">
            <div class="section-kicker">Lend</div>
            <h2 class="section-title">Lend to people you actually know something about.</h2>
            <p class="section-subtitle">
              See who you are speaking to, what their plans are, and decide for yourself whether the risk
              makes sense.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="section-grid">
            <div class="card">
              <div class="card-title">See the person behind the request</div>
              <p>
                Identity-verified profiles include essential background information so you are not lending
                into a void. You decide which requests deserve your attention.
              </p>
            </div>
            <div class="card">
              <div class="card-title">Set your own boundaries</div>
              <p>
                Define what kind of borrowers, timelines, and risk levels you are open to. You can keep
                your participation small and focused, or gradually expand.
              </p>
            </div>
            <div class="card">
              <div class="card-title">Stay in control</div>
              <p>
                You choose the amount, the terms, and the conditions you are comfortable with. AmicBridge
                never touches your funds and never signs on your behalf.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Strategy -->
      <section id="strategy" class="section">
        <div class="container">
          <div class="section-header">
            <div class="section-kicker">Strategy</div>
            <h2 class="section-title">A long-term trust network, not a quick-volume platform.</h2>
            <p class="section-subtitle">
              The aim is to grow a focused network of serious members, then gradually expand into new
              private financing relationships where identity and reputation matter.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="section-grid">
            <div class="card">
              <div class="card-title">Start with private lending</div>
              <p>
                Phase one focuses on person-to-person lending between identity-verified members. Clear,
                small-scale requests build trust and experience.
              </p>
            </div>
            <div class="card">
              <div class="card-title">Grow a reputation graph</div>
              <p>
                Over time, a history of responsible behaviour forms a reputation layer. This can support
                more advanced private financing opportunities.
              </p>
            </div>
            <div class="card">
              <div class="card-title">Expand carefully</div>
              <p>
                Future steps may include small business financing, private investing, or additional tools
                for risk analysis—always with identity and transparency at the core.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Disclaimer -->
      <section class="disclaimer">
        <div class="container">
          <div class="disclaimer-inner">
            <strong>Important information.</strong>
            <br />
            AmicBridge is a private peer-to-peer network. It does not act as a bank or broker, does not
            hold or manage funds, and does not guarantee repayment, returns, or matches. All agreements,
            transfers, and assessments are made directly between members, who remain fully responsible for
            their own decisions and any legal or tax obligations. Nothing on this site is financial advice.
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>
    </main>

    <!-- Footer -->
    <footer class="footer" id="contact">
      <div class="container footer-inner">
        <div>
          &copy; <!-- update year as needed --> 2025 AmicBridge. All rights reserved.
        </div>
        <div class="footer-links">
          <span>Oslo, Norway</span>
          <a href="mailto:contact@amicbridge.com">contact@amicbridge.com</a>
          <a href="#">Terms</a>
          <a href="#">Privacy</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </footer>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
